Lesson 3: Writing News
This lesson plan is the third of a series of six that explain the news-making process followed by professional journalists. OBJECTIVESTo understand: The structure and writing style of a news report Why there are School Report rules about child protection LESSON 3: ACTIVITIES AND RESOURCES
